Rick D. Damron 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Operating Officer at LOWE'S COMPANIES INC, Rick D. Damron  made $4,700,659 in total compensation.  Of this total $790,000 was received as a salary, $628,579 was received as a bonus, $805,273 was received in stock options, $2,403,706 was awarded as stock and $73,101 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


